        ],
        "description": "# v2.product.update_item\n\nUse this endpoint to update item information.\n\n## Request Parameters\n\n| Name | Type | Required | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| description | string | False | Description of item. |\n| weight | float | False | Weight of item. |\n| pre_order | object | False | Pre Order setting. |\n| days_to_ship | int | True | Days to ship. |\n| is_pre_order | boolean | True | Whether the item is pre order. |\n| item_name | string | False | Item name. |\n| attribute_list | object\\[\\] | False | Item attributes. |\n| attribute_id | int | True | ID of attribute. |\n| attribute_value_list | object\\[\\] | False |  |\n| value_id | int | True | ID of attribute value. In the following cases, the value id needs to be uploaded as 0, and original_value_name is mandatory, needs to be filled in customized value. (1) AttributeInputType is TEXT_FILED; (2) AttributeInputType is COMBO_BOX or MULTIPLE_SELECT_COMBO_BOX, and the seller want to fill in a customized value. |\n| original_value_name | string | False | Value name. original_value_name from produc.get_attributes api. If value id=0, this field is required. If AttributeType is DATE_TYPE or TIMESTAMP_TYPE, you can upload timestamp(string type) as the original_value_name. |\n| value_unit | string | False | Unit of attribute value (quantitative attribute only). |\n| image | object | False | Images of item. |\n| image_id_list | object\\[\\] | True | Image ID. |\n| item_sku | string | False | SKU tag for item. |\n| item_status | string | False | Item status, could be UNLIST or NORMAL. |\n| logistic_info | object\\[\\] | False | Logistic channel setting. |\n| size_id | int | False | Size ID. |\n| shipping_fee | float | False | Shipping fee. |\n| enabled | boolean | True | Whether the channel is enabled for this item. |\n| logistic_id | int | True | ID of logistics channel. |\n| is_free | boolean | False | Whether cover shipping fee for buyer. |\n| wholesale | object\\[\\] | False |   <br>  <br>Wholesale setting.  <br>  <br>If you want to delete it, please pass it with blank.  <br>  <br>  <br> |\n| min_count | int | True | Minimum count of this tier. |\n| unit_price | float | True |   <br>  <br>Price of this tier.  <br>  <br>  <br>  <br>For SG/MY/BR/MX/PL/ES/AR seller: Sellers can set the price with two decimal place, other regions can only set the price as an integer.  <br>  <br>  <br> |\n| max_count | int | True | Maximum count of this tier. |\n| item_id | int | True | ID of item. |\n| category_id | int | False | ID of category. |\n| dimension | object | False | Dimension of item. |\n| package_height | int | True |   <br>  <br>Height of package, unit is cm.  <br>  <br> |\n| package_length | int | True |   <br>  <br>Length of package, unit is cm.  <br>  <br> |\n| package_width | int | True |   <br>  <br>Width of package, unit is cm.  <br>  <br> |\n| condition | string | False | Condition of item, could be NEW or USED. |\n| video_upload_id | string | False |   <br>  <br>Video upload ID returned from video uploading API.  <br>  <br>If you want to delete it, please pass it with blank.  <br>  <br>  <br> |\n| brand | object | False |  |\n| brand_id | int | False | Id of brand. |\n| item_dangerous | int | False | This field is only applicable for local sellers in Indonesia and Malaysia. Use this field to identify whether a product is a dangerous product. 0 for non-dangerous product and 1 for dangerous product. For more information, please visit the market's respective Seller Education Hub. |\n| tax_info | object | False | Tax information |\n| ncm | string | False | Mercosur Common Nomenclature, it is a convention between Mercosur member countries to easily recognize goods, services and productive factors negotiated among themselves. |\n| same_state_cfop | string | False | Tax Code of Operations and Installments for orders that seller and buyer are in the same state. It identifies a specific operation by category at the time of issuing the invoice. |\n| diff_state_cfop | string | False | Tax Code of Operations and Installments for orders that seller and buyer are in different states. It identifies a specific operation by category at the time of issuing the invoice. |\n| csosn | string | False | Code of Operation Status \u2013 Simples Nacional, code for company operations to identify the origin of the goods and the taxation regime of the operations. |\n| origin | string | False | Product source, domestic or foreig |\n| cest | string | False | (BR region) |\n| measure_unit | string | False | (BR region) |\n| invoice_option | string | False | Value shuold be one of NO_INVOICES VAT_MARGIN_SCHEME_INVOICES VAT_INVOICES NON_VAT_INVOICES and if value is NON_VAT_INVOICE vat_rate should be null (PL region) |\n| vat_rate | string | False | Value should be one of 0% 5% 8% 23% NO_VAT_RATE (PL region) |\n| hs_code | string | False | HS Code. (Only for IN region) |\n| tax_code | string | False | Tax Code. (Only for IN region) |\n| complaint_policy | object | False | Complaint Policy for item. Only required for local PL sellers, ignored otherwise. |\n| warranty_time | string | False | Value should be in one of ONE_YEAR TWO_YEARS OVER_TWO_YEARS. |\n| exclude_entrepreneur_warranty | boolean | False | If True means \"I exclude warranty complaints for entrepreneur\" |\n| complaint_address_id | int | False | Address for complaint. Fetch available addresses using v2.logistics.get_address_list, and use address_id returned from it. |\n| additional_information | string | False | Additional information for warranty claim. Should be less than 1000 characters. |\n| description_info | object | False | New description field. Only whitelist sellers can use it. If you use the field, please upload the description_type=extended otherwise api will return error. If you don't use this field, you don't need to upload the description_type or upload description_type=normal |\n| extended_description | object | False | If description_type is extended , description information should be set by this field. |\n| field_list | object\\[\\] | False | Field of extended description. |\n| field_type | string | False | Type of extended description field: values: See Data Definition- description_field_type (text , image). |\n| text | string | False | If field_type is text, text information will be set by this field. |\n| image_info | object | False | If field_type is image, image url will be set by this field. |\n| image_id | string | False | Image id. |\n| description_type | string | False |   <br>  <br>description_type (normal , extended). If you want to use extended_description or change description type ,this field must be inputed  <br>  <br> |\n\n**More info at:** [Update Item](https://open.shopee.com/documents/v2/v2.product.update_item?module=89&type=1)",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "item_id": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "price_list": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "original_price": {
                          "type": "integer"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "item_id": 1810408,
                "price_list": [
                  {
                    "original_price": 100
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v2/product/update_stock": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "update_stock",
        "operationId": "update_stock",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code. Empty string means success."
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error message details."
                    },
                    "request_id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Unique request identifier for debugging."
                    },
                    "response": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "description": "Response payload."
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "tags": [
          "Product"
        ],
        "description": "Use this to update the stock of the products",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "item_id": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "stock_list": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "model_id": {
                          "type": "integer"
                        },
                        "normal_stock": {
                          "type": "integer"
                        },
                        "seller_stock": {
                          "type": "array",
                          "items": {
                            "type": "object",
                            "properties": {
                              "location_id": {
                                "type": "string"
                              },
                              "stock": {
                                "type": "integer"
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "item_id": 19323880620,
                "stock_list": [
                  {
                    "model_id": 0,
                    "normal_stock": 0,
                    "seller_stock": [
                      {
                        "location_id": "MX000000Z",
                        "stock": 400
                      },
                      {
                        "location_id": "MX000001Z",
                        "stock": 345
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v2/shop/auth_partner": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "Get Authorization URL",
        "operationId": "get_auth_url",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Successful response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "error": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error code. Empty string means success."
                    },
                    "message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Error message details."
                    },
                    "request_id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Unique request identifier for debugging."
                    },
                    "response": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "description": "Response payload."
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "redirect",
            "in": "query",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "example": "http://localhost:8000/shopee/auth"
          }
        ],
        "tags": [
          "Auth"
        ],
        "description": "Generate the authorization URL for a shop to authorize the partner application. Redirect sellers to this URL to initiate the OAuth flow."
      }
    },
